room_title: Escape room "The Fortune Teller" by Level Games in Los Angeles
room_description: Curiosity leads you to pay a visit to a local fortune teller. As the tarot cards reveal their message -- to your dismay -- the news is not good. You discover that your fate is connected to an impending disaster. Don't worry though, you have a chance to change your destiny! Will you face the challenge and rectify your future?
